sequenceDiagram
    participant Browser
    participant Server as MyHTTPServer
    participant Parser as RequestParser
    participant Servlet
    participant State as Config/Topics/View

    Browser->>Server: HTTP request
    Server->>Parser: parseRequest(reader)
    Parser-->>Server: RequestInfo
    Server->>Server: find longest URI prefix for method
    Server->>Servlet: handle(RequestInfo, OutputStream)
    Servlet->>State: read or mutate runtime state
    State-->>Servlet: result HTML or notice
    Servlet-->>Browser: HTTP response
